                     <interp inst="t17260831-23-off108" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17260831-23-off108" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               privately stealing 63 Yards of Modena, and Pink Italian Mantua, value 15 l. the Goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17260831-23-victim155" type="victimName">
                           Joshua 
                           Feary 
                        <interp inst="t17260831-23-victim155" type="surname" value="Feary"></interp>
